reviewText: Three terribly bad movies in this package, so don't bother.  None of them are worth watching, much less paying for.  You would think they would have put one decent movie in the bunch.
Good movies about life in the army.......
Just want to point out that Straight Into Darkness is not a Nazi Zombie movie, despite the cover art which seems to show living dead Nazis.  Very disappointing for us expecting the next Zombie Lake.
